body:
If that d/c player is in a premade, players of the premade can&#039;t take part in the vote to reform. I know it sounds rude, but if it isn&#039;t like this, every premade with a d/c will go something like this..

&quot;Hey Taric is d/c, we should reform&quot;

&quot;Nah, his computer just crashed, he&#039;ll be back&quot;

*15 minutes and 36 deaths later*

&quot;A summoner has reconnected&quot;

I mean not every game is like this but I hate the risk of it happening, please Riot.
